data.description: The Walsh is a 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom that will embrace you and family with comfort, while still providing a spacious open flow throughout. The exquisitely designed kitchen/dining area provides a substantial amount of counter top space, and storage. All bedrooms are conveniently located. You will be amazed at the quality the builder has put into every aspect from the materials to the fixtures. The incentives of buying this new home are to much to list.
